headline: The Weekly Closeout: Big 5 Sporting Goods sold, NRF goes up against New York
summary: The retailer was acquired by Worldwide Golf and Capitol Hill Group. Meanwhile, the National Retail Federation took aim at New York's new law requiring algorithmic pricing disclosures.

headline: US retailer Ulta Beauty enters UK market with Space NK acquisition
summary: The acquisition was financed using Ulta Beauty's available cash and its existing credit facility.
